quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  41,30,"Pellet, wi'uɓe ɓeen : "Joomi amen ko Allah", refti ɓe tabiti; Malaa'ika'en hino jippoo e maɓɓe (wiide): "Wota on hulu, wota on suno; wewliree Aljanna, on mo wonanoɗon fodeede."
  41,31,"Ko minen ngoni ni wallooɓe on ɓeen ka nguurndam aduna e ka La'akara. Hino woodani on ton, kala ko woŋkiiji mon wooɗetee, hino woodani ton, kala ko noddoton,"
  41,32,"ko maraari, immorde e kaforoore, Hinnotooɗo"."
  41,33,"Hara ko hommbo ɓuri moƴƴude konngol, wano on nodduɗo e fii Allah, o golli moƴƴere, o wi'i: "miin, ko e juulɓe ɓen mi njiyaa?"."
  41,34,"Moƴƴere ndeen fotataa e bone on. Duñir (golle bonɗe ɗen) kon ko ɓuri moƴƴude; e jaka yoo, on mo ngayngu woni hakkunde maa e mum, himo wa'ita wa giɗo saɗtuɗo giggol."
  41,35,"Kono hawrataa e ɗuum, si wonaa muññiiɓe ɓen; hawrataa e ɗuum, si wonaa jom geɗal mawnungal."
  41,36,"Si sowinsinoore arii heɓude ma immorde e seytaane, moolor Allah. Kaŋko ko O Nanoowo, gannduɗo."
  41,37,"Hino jiyaa e Ma'andeeji makko ɗin, jemma on e ñalawma on, e na'ange ngen e lewru ndun. Wota on cujjan na'ange ngen wonaa kadi lewru ndun. Cujjanee Allah, takɗo ɗi On, si wonii ko Kaŋko ndewoton."
  41,38,"Si ɓe townitike, ɓeen wonɓe ka Joomi maa kan, hiɓe cubbunhinorana mo jemma e ñalawma, hara ɓe haaɓataa."